description: Seeed Studio has expanded its XIAO MG24 and XIAO MG24 Sense development board lineup with new variants, including pre-soldered versions and 3PCS packs. These additions provide more flexibility for developers working on IoT and Matter-based projects, streamlining prototyping and small-scale production. title: Silicon Labs-Based XIAO MG24 Series Expands with New Pre-Soldered and Multi-Pack Versions
